{"tid":441160,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要用雞呢種動物形容妓女","createTime":"2017-10-19T11:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T02:04:12.000Z","uid":95520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"99d63359884f92bc9bee810fd2e0891d02123515","tid":441160,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:55:10.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69cdacbbe4c7544b8c553b671acb5a8afd8c9a23","tid":441160,"uid":51819,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"普通話：「召妓」"},{"pid":"64305a3e8e7d410dd6c55d8766c670527a041035","tid":441160,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:40:35.000Z","msg":"認真，同普通話有關係？妓，雞？"},{"pid":"a5902d4b4cab318bab7d4551e3beabd4a06f2902","tid":441160,"uid":136430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:45:19.000Z","msg":"妓雞普通話同聲同韻"},{"pid":"e69a1c548f2b1c2746477fd13dc613bb5cbf1485","tid":441160,"uid":56240,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:45:48.000Z","msg":"此貼必火，則他媽牛b"},{"pid":"01f711bd58d477a3fbe9a8803cb505e0ee30f63b","tid":441160,"uid":30377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通話：「召妓」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9dafeb66358f4fcb49f3e4ab9835feee7b38dc","tid":441160,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:56:09.000Z","msg":"食飽，乜乜乜乜，同埋訓"},{"pid":"72b9c39348e4fb3691f9d1733b30e3dadc120e90","tid":441160,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:57:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>普通話：「召妓」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以叫雞係炒蝗語？"},{"pid":"d11042d9314161576288facbf6198bd39c17bfdb","tid":441160,"uid":51819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>普通話：「召妓」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以叫雞係炒蝗語？</blockquote><br />\n但都可能係香港（最少係粵語文化區域）出現。<br />\n以前香港人有錢，返大陸叫雞，嗰到啲人用普通話問：「是不是要召妓」<br />\n而普通話上叫雞又同召妓同音<br />\n噉班返開大陸叫雞嘅死廢老咪用叫雞做暗號<br />\n噉唔算抄嘅 算係粵語文化"},{"pid":"3c93cdd555b8fca77064c96ae1836d01c1b7fb5c","tid":441160,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T21:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>普通話：「召妓」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以叫雞係炒蝗語？</blockquote><br />\n但都可能係香港（最少係粵語文化區域）出現。<br />\n以前香港人有錢，返大陸叫雞，嗰到啲人用普通話問：「是不是要召妓」<br />\n而普通話上叫雞又同召妓同音<br />\n噉班返開大陸叫雞嘅死廢老咪用叫雞做暗號<br />\n噉唔算抄嘅 算係粵語文化</blockquote><br />\n咁叫鴨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda308030eb2448373dfb09409fe395030bfc876","tid":441160,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T00:25:00.000Z","msg":"本地禁止散養家禽，已經好少人知道「🐓」嘅真正形態。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果就演變成「對某性別人士」嘅禁字之一。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff3a630f949594efe3a162f6e0b928ee9793357","tid":441160,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>普通話：「召妓」</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以叫雞係炒蝗語？</blockquote><br />\n但都可能係香港（最少係粵語文化區域）出現。<br />\n以前香港人有錢，返大陸叫雞，嗰到啲人用普通話問：「是不是要召妓」<br />\n而普通話上叫雞又同召妓同音<br />\n噉班返開大陸叫雞嘅死廢老咪用叫雞做暗號<br />\n噉唔算抄嘅 算係粵語文化</blockquote><br />\n普通話召妓 用廣東話讀出嚟讀叫雞 <br />\n好似英文taxi 用廣東話讀出嚟讀的士<br />\n但你唔會話的士係英文掛"},{"pid":"d06caf199395d268d7e2adfa880297ecc1497983","tid":441160,"uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"我認真答你<br />\n<br />\n古時候，世界上只有男人，<br />\n<br />\n有個人30歲做左魔法師，覺得咁樣既世界好悶，<br />\n<br />\n就將一個農場既雞變曬做女人，不過d女人好貪錢，要比錢佢地先肯扑野，<br />\n<br />\n其他魔法師見幾盞鬼，就不斷將d雞變做女人<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家眼見既女人都係雞"},{"pid":"8fbada9c9a8aef0c0cc77e674c0906290c1f56ea","tid":441160,"uid":65587,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認真答你<br />\n<br />\n古時候，世界上只有男人，<br />\n<br />\n有個人30歲做左魔法師，覺得咁樣既世界好悶，<br />\n<br />\n就將一個農場既雞變曬做女人，不過d女人好貪錢，要比錢佢地先肯扑野，<br />\n<br />\n其他魔法師見幾盞鬼，就不斷將d雞變做女人<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家眼見既女人都係雞</blockquote><br />\n好多謝呢位黎自庇護工場既朋友為大家帶黎咁精彩既演出."},{"pid":"fe491bbbbc8424d029c183230a9c462ee97c672f","tid":441160,"uid":26783,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我認真答你<br />\n<br />\n古時候，世界上只有男人，<br />\n<br />\n有個人30歲做左魔法師，覺得咁樣既世界好悶，<br />\n<br />\n就將一個農場既雞變曬做女人，不過d女人好貪錢，要比錢佢地先肯扑野，<br />\n<br />\n其他魔法師見幾盞鬼，就不斷將d雞變做女人<br />\n<br />\n所以宜家眼見既女人都係雞</blockquote><br />\n=.="},{"pid":"810e32cea9ce5c1c3ef313f61b613030b3ee1271","tid":441160,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普通話：「召妓」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正解"}]}